data.description: This charming home boast 1600 sq ft of living space, offering a comfortable and spacious enviroment. With 3 bdrm and 2 1/2 baths this home provides ample room. Nestled in the beautiful Butte's subdivision, this home enjoys the benefits of a gated community, providing security and peace of mind. Situated on a carner lot, this property is tastefully landscaped, enhancing its curb appeal and creating an inviting atmosphere. The full fenced backyard is a gardners dream, offering a great space to cultivate your own oasis. The master bedroom features a private bath, ensuring convenience and privacy. Don't miss the extraordinary opportunity to own a home in this fantastic neighborhood.  **REDUCED PRICE, MOTIVATED SELLERS**
